text: Winckler is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Charles Winckler (1867–1932), Danish athlete and tug of war competitor *Cindy Winckler (born 1950), the Iowa State Representative from the 86th District *Gustav Winckler *Heinz Winckler *Jutta Hering-Winckler (born 1948), lawyer and patron of music *Hugo Winckler, archaeologist *Martin Winckler (born 1955), French writer ==See also== *Winkler (surname)
